FROM title t, movie_companies mc, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.kind_id  =  3 AND t.production_year  =  1999 AND mc.company_id  <  1021 AND mc.company_type_id  =  2
